#: ../../source/Installation.rst:23
msgid "Step 2: Install"
msgstr "第 2 步:安装"

#: ../../source/Installation.rst:25
msgid ""
"A dedicated `conda environment <https://conda.io/projects/conda/en/latest"
"/user-guide/tasks/manage-environments.html>`_ is recommended so the "
"optimization-solver dependencies stay isolated:"
msgstr ""
"建议使用单独的 `conda 环境 <https://conda.io/projects/conda/en/latest/user-"
"guide/tasks/manage-environments.html>`_,以便隔离求解器依赖:"

#: ../../source/Installation.rst:36
msgid ""
"``pip install -e .`` installs PREP-SHOT itself in editable mode AND pulls"
" in every runtime dependency declared in ``pyproject.toml``. The default "
"solver `HiGHS <https://highs.dev/>`_ is installed automatically as a "
"wheel; commercial solvers need a separate install and a ``solver`` change"
" in the scenario's ``config.json``."
msgstr ""
"``pip install -e .`` 会以可编辑模式安装 PREP-SHOT,并自动安装 ``pyproject.toml`` "
"中声明的所有运行时依赖。默认求解器 `HiGHS <https://highs.dev/>`_ 以 wheel "
"形式自动安装;商用求解器需另行安装,并在算例的 ``config.json`` 中修改 ``solver`` 字段。"

