#: ../../source/Installation.rst:122
msgid "Step 3: Run a scenario"
msgstr "第 3 步:运行算例"

#: ../../source/Installation.rst:124
msgid ""
"Each subdirectory of ``examples/`` is a self-contained scenario. Pick one"
" and run from inside it; see :doc:`Quickstart` for a hands-on walkthrough"
" on the ``three_zone`` dataset."
msgstr ""
"``examples/`` 下的每个子目录都是一个自包含的算例。任选其一,进入该目录运行;参见 :doc:`Quickstart` 对 "
"``three_zone`` 数据集的完整动手演练。"

#: ../../source/Installation.rst:133
msgid ""
"Three scenarios ship with the repo: ``three_zone`` (synthetic 3-zone, "
"used by :doc:`Quickstart`), ``southeast_asia`` (Lower Mekong, 5 "
"countries, 57 reservoirs), and ``thailand`` (single-zone with 13 Mekong-"
"basin reservoirs)."
msgstr ""
"仓库随附三个算例:``three_zone`` (人工合成的 3 区域算例,被 :doc:`Quickstart` "
"使用)、``southeast_asia`` (湄公河下游,5 个国家,57 座水库)、``thailand`` (单一区域,13 "
"座湄公河流域水库)。"

#: ../../source/Installation.rst:138
msgid ""
"To run your own scenario, copy ``examples/three_zone/`` as a starting "
"template and edit ``input/*.csv`` + ``config.json``."
msgstr ""
"如要运行自定义算例,可复制 ``examples/three_zone/`` 作为起始模板,然后编辑 ``input/*.csv`` 与 "
"``config.json``。"

#: ../../source/Installation.rst:143
msgid "Step 4: Use PREP-SHOT as a Python library"
msgstr "第 4 步:作为 Python 库使用 PREP-SHOT"

#: ../../source/Installation.rst:145
msgid ""
"After ``pip install -e .``, PREP-SHOT can be imported and driven directly"
" from your own Python code. The simplest entry point is "
"``prepshot.cli.main``, which mirrors the ``prepshot`` console script and "
"runs a full build-solve-save cycle on a directory containing "
"``config.json`` and ``params.json``:"
msgstr ""
"在执行 ``pip install -e .`` 之后,可以直接从你自己的 Python 代码中导入和驱动 PREP-SHOT。最简单的入口是 "
"``prepshot.cli.main``,它与 ``prepshot`` 命令行脚本等价,会在含有 ``config.json`` 与 "
"``params.json`` 的目录上完整执行 \"建模—求解—保存\" 全过程:"

#: ../../source/Installation.rst:159
msgid ""
"For finer-grained control -- multiple scenarios in the same Python "
"process, inspecting the model after solving, skipping the default Excel "
"output -- use the lower-level functions:"
msgstr "如需更精细的控制——同一 Python 进程中运行多个算例、求解后查看模型、跳过默认 Excel 输出——可使用更底层的函数:"

#: ../../source/Installation.rst:179
msgid ""
"The Python API is stable across the v1.x series; it is the recommended "
"surface for downstream code that depends on PREP-SHOT. See "
":doc:`Stability` for the full stability policy."
msgstr ""
"Python API 在整个 v1.x 系列保持稳定,是依赖 PREP-SHOT 的下游代码推荐使用的接口。完整的稳定性政策参见 "
":doc:`Stability`。"

